                  <provenance>The person who originally owned the manuscript is <persName ref="PRS15303NewayaSellase"><roleName type="title">ʾAbuna</roleName>
                     Nǝwāya Śǝllāse</persName>. His name has been fully or partly erased from the supplication on <locus target="#122v"/> and from <ref target="#coloph1"/>. 
                     Also, the name of the church to which he originally donated the book was erased.
                     The name of <persName ref="PRS15304GabraEgzi"><roleName type="title">ʾAbuna</roleName> Gabra ʾƎgziʾ</persName>
                     was erased from the supplication on <locus target="#122v"/>, from <ref target="#coloph1"/>, and from <ref target="#a1"/>, written by a secondary hand. 
                     Members of his family are mentioned in <ref target="#a1"/>. <persName role="donor" ref="PRS15305GabraMaryam"><roleName type="title">ʾAbuna</roleName> Gabra Māryām</persName> 
                     appears as the donor in <ref target="#a2"/>. His family members are also mentioned. 
